#. <section class="sutta" id="sn9.7"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn9.7:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 9"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 9"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn9.7:0.2"
msgid "1. Vanavagga"
msgstr "1. In the Woods"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn9.7:0.3"
msgid "7. Nāgadattasutta"
msgstr "7. With Nāgadatta"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts1ed" id="pts1ed1.201"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn9.7:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ āyasmā nāgadatto kosalesu viharati aññatarasmiṃ vanasaṇḍe."
msgstr ""
"At one time Venerable Nāgadatta was staying in the land of the Kosalans in a "
"certain forest grove."

msgctxt "sn9.7:1.2"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena āyasmā nāgadatto atikālena gāmaṃ pavisati, atidivā "
"paṭikkamati."
msgstr ""
"Now at that time Venerable Nāgadatta had been entering the village too early "
"and returning late in the day."

msgctxt "sn9.7:1.3"
msgid ""
"Atha kho yā tasmiṃ vanasaṇḍe adhivatthā devatā āyasmato nāgadattassa "
"anukampikā atthakāmā āyasmantaṃ nāgadattaṃ saṃvejetukāmā yenāyasmā nāgadatto "
"tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā āyasmantaṃ nāgadattaṃ gāthāhi ajjhabhāsi:"
msgstr ""
"Then the deity haunting that forest had compassion for Nāgadatta, wanting "
"what’s best for him. So they approached him wanting to stir him up, and "
"recited these verses:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn9.7:2.1"
msgid "“Kāle pavisa nāgadatta,"
msgstr "“Entering too early,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn9.7:2.2"
msgid "Divā ca āgantvā ativelacārī;"
msgstr "and returning after spending too much of the day,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn9.7:2.3"
msgid "Saṃsaṭṭho gahaṭṭhehi,"
msgstr "Nāgadatta socializes with lay people,"

# Following BB’s proposed readings.
#. <br>
msgctxt "sn9.7:2.4"
msgid "Samānasukhadukkho."
msgstr "sharing their joys and sorrows."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.433"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn9.7:3.1"
msgid "Bhāyāmi nāgadattaṃ suppagabbhaṃ,"
msgstr "I’m afraid for Nāgadatta; he’s so reckless"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn9.7:3.2"
msgid "Kulesu vinibaddhaṃ;"
msgstr "in his attachment to families."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn9.7:3.3"
msgid "Mā heva maccurañño balavato,"
msgstr "May he not come under the King of Death’s power,"

#. <br>
#. VAR: vasaṃ upesī”ti → vasamesīti (bj, s1-3, km) | vasam eyyā ti (pts1-2)
msgctxt "sn9.7:3.4"
msgid "Antakassa vasaṃ upesī”ti."
msgstr "under the sway of the Terminator!”"

#. </p></blockquote><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn9.7:4.1"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā nāgadatto tāya devatāya saṃvejito saṃvegamāpādīti."
msgstr "Stirred up by that deity, Venerable Nāgadatta came to his senses."
